## Exercise 06 — Differentiation Breakdown

### 📝 Your Answers

| What the Space Does | EIW Position |
|---|---|
| Fantasy is escapism — a retreat from reality | Fantasy is a destination. The best fantasy is truer than true — what's real on Middle Earth is real everywhere, in every era |
| Using AI in your creative process is cheating | AI is a totem of human knowledge. Every writer uses every tool available. It's not whether you use it — it's how. |
| Video games are a waste of time | Games create real connections, real memories, real communities. They are significant works of art and deeply human. |
| I'm not religious so mythology doesn't apply to me | You don't get to opt out. Myths are operating systems — if you're not aware of yours you'll inherit one without knowing it. Try on a different one and you'll finally see which one your computer is already running. |
| Declare the ambition only after the world validates your talent | You're not supposed to say it out loud before you've earned it. I'm saying it anyway. |

